-- attested sensor (Familiar / Augur) promotes the entry to 'active' and
-- appends the attestation.

-- Idempotency: re-running this migration on a populated registry would
-- issue NEW OAI IDs (sequence advances), creating duplicates. The guard
-- below short-circuits if any seed-shaped reserved rows already exist.

